Author: lostandlonley333
Text: I sympathise with this so much. Im sorry for your pain, sounds like your torn between recovery (even though the calories you described would still be a deficiency) and staying with the ED. I encourage you to keep eating, everyone's body needs to be fed and there's no need to feel guilty for it. My boyfriend is the same, if you feel like you need someone to cent to seeing a psychologist personally helped me a lot.
